{"title":"客里","authors":["如澄"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":7,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"客里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天涯思乡客  如澄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"客里春光奈若何，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故园应是绿婆娑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄鹂此日鸣深树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朗月何时照碧河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨同舟欢会少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死生共济苦离多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年北望空惆怅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卅载乡思鬓已皤。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}